tor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67942c1747c3d0e3c305f502c9fdc4636d58c150","tid":217453,"uid":107765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T19:38:28.000Z","msg":"tesla 用摩打個喎老世"},{"pid":"b57971051fe44a63bb8137cf0effbf625dc49c98","tid":217453,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:01:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>tesla 用摩打個喎老世</blockquote><br />\n睇你點定義engine"},{"pid":"a4f3ba402784896df29523d99587ba6667022b9e","tid":217453,"uid":33190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>tesla 用摩打個喎老世</blockquote><br />\n睇你點定義engine</blockquote><br />\nmotor同engine唔同woo"},{"pid":"53500e3fc098275a523d21201b489ff3c8b445a7","tid":217453,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Tesla都無引擎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEngine: a machine with moving parts that converts power into motion.</blockquote><br />\n正確啲講果個叫motor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時候真係睇個官點定義engine"},{"pid":"e3ae03b453a7a0013a6ee10d76ea38cdd31a1664","tid":217453,"uid":109608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:06:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Tesla都無引擎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEngine: a machine with moving parts that converts power into motion.</blockquote><br />\n正確啲講果個叫motor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時候真係睇個官點定義engine</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔踩腳踏個摩打唔會轉（好似係）"},{"pid":"754da00c10ce4ff4714a1483442d245f3104f78d","tid":217453,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>