中學如果有讀physic果陣已經講過engine同motor既分別，你應該唔係讀physics，其實都幾明確"},{"pid":"e9d4a06303f58449c1517848a656c47317d05d7f","tid":217453,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:13:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Tesla都無引擎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEngine: a machine with moving parts that converts power into motion.</blockquote><br />\n正確啲講果個叫motor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時候真係睇個官點定義engine</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/air/prob_solutions/idling_prohibition.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epd.gov.hk%2Fepd%2Ftc_chi%2Fenvironmentinhk%2Fair%2Fprob_solutions%2Fidling_prohibition.html&d=mfTbPTXtdXcWugdQC%2B6BDiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=31c81dcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/air/prob_solutions/idling_prohibition.html</a><br />\n內燃引擎指燃料在內燃燒室內燃燒的引擎。<br />\n定義左, 好明顯純電車入面冇燃料燃燒</blockquote><br />\nthanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋下面都講左<br />\n<br />\n3. 所有裝置有以汽油、柴油或石油氣等為燃料驅動的內燃引擎的汽車，以及正在燃燒這些燃料的混合動力車輛。由於電動車輛和只有電動馬達在運行的混合動力車輛不會產生廢氣，因此停車熄匙規定對它們並不適用"},{"pid":"13b23041fd962b84d801351edfab7dfa442c4368","tid":217453,"uid":109608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T20:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Tesla都無引擎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nEngine: a machine with moving parts that converts power into motion.</blockquote><br />\n正確啲講果個叫motor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到時候真係睇個官點定義engine</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epd.gov.hk/epd/tc_chi/environmentinhk/air/prob_solutions/idling_prohibition.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.